
   ABILITY:  block <dir>
   LEVEL:    Thug
   COST:     Low graft

   DESCRIPTION:
     Stop any player in the same room as you from moving in
     <dir> unless they first make payment to you.  The payment
     will be converted to graft and distributed amongst the
     family.  NOTE: Players that have paid protection will not
     be affected by this ability.  See 'mhelp protect'.

